<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mythology_of_Lost&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFKaye">Kaye, Sharon M. <i><a href="http://www.blackwellpublishing.com/book.asp?ref=9781405163156" class="external text" title="http://www.blackwellpublishing.com/book.asp?ref=9781405163156" rel="nofollow">Lost and Philosophy: The Island Has Its Reasons</a></i>. The Blackwell Philosophy and Pop Culture Series (1 ed.). <a href="/wiki/Blackwell_Publishing" title="Blackwell Publishing">Blackwell Publishing</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1405163151" class="internal">ISBN 1405163151</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.blackwellpublishing.com/book.asp?ref=9781405163156" class="external free" title="http://www.blackwellpublishing.com/book.asp?ref=9781405163156" rel="nofollow">http://www.blackwellpublishing.com/book.asp?ref=9781405163156</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-02-07</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Lost+and+Philosophy%3A+The+Island+Has+Its+Reasons&amp;rft.aulast=Kaye&amp;rft.aufirst=Sharon+M&amp;rft.au=Kaye%2C+Sharon+M&amp;rft.series=The+Blackwell+Philosophy+and+Pop+Culture+Series&amp;rft.edition=1&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BBlackwell+Publishing%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=1405163151&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blackwellpublishing.com%2Fbook.asp%3Fref%3D9781405163156&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mythology_of_Lost"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
